{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58a5e066e9","title":"大字报——整风运动有感","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1d14d15bf8","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"58a5e066e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1aceba35d0","name":"电力部"},{"id":"834fa85ae4","name":"栾忠政"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"52c9a2d553","type":"title","text":"大字报——整风运动有感","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"d768c24776","type":"authors","text":"电力部栾忠政","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"dadba12596","type":"subtitle","text":"（栾忠政：北京电力设计分院线路室技术员）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"848f236878","type":"paragraph","text":"1．牛顿三大运动定律在过去政治生活中的运用。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"5f78fe4004","type":"paragraph","text":"第一定律：动者恒动，静者恒静。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"c629d004ae","type":"paragraph","text":"运用：进步的永远进步，落后的永远是落后的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"3279985c40","type":"paragraph","text":"第二定律：作用力等于物体质量乘上加速度。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"a6e8f567b4","type":"paragraph","text":"运用：共产党员的特权等于党员的恶劣品质乘上拍马屁的加速度。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"33e46d3828","type":"paragraph","text":"第三定律：作用力等于反作用力。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"3ece0bf436","type":"paragraph","text":"运用：谁提的意见最多，谁受的打击和报复也就越多。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"d46b9a7def","type":"paragraph","text":"2．某些共产党员的三大作用：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"a83d263ec7","type":"paragraph","text":"检波、放大和失真。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"54f64f4515","type":"paragraph","text":"3．论实事求是：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"25ae22fadf","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反运动时党中央估计全国有5％的反革命份子，全国6亿人×5％＝3000万反革命份子，结果在肃反运动中全国查出8万个反革命份子（注1）。3000万除以8万等于375，即扩大了375倍。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"d61b9edea1","type":"paragraph","text":"试问这叫实事求是吗？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"511f8f9d62","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，在肃反运动中除了上述8万反革命份子以外，你知道被逼自杀、精神失常、神经衰弱和失眠的人又有多少？谁能解答这个问题？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"76bd93aee1","type":"paragraph","text":"（注1）根据党中央书记邓小平在某次会议上的报告，其中包括被宽大处理的反革命份子。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"},{"id":"49a410fc1b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《想一想，对不对》（电力工业部整风办公室编印，1957年7月）。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9"}],"page":{"id":"84ac191925","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58a5e066e9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}